<br>
I used the word 'review' in a specific copntext.  Only the 2 items would be reviewed at all.<br>
<br>
While, it might cause hurt feelings, we would have to look at the job they did, wouldn't we?  <br>
<br>
Personally, I'm not thinking that any one wouldn't have done a good job, but we'd have to at least look at the job performance.  We'd be stupid not to.  If we don't look at it we're creating a 'civil service' like envioronment in that once you're in, you can never be replaced.<br>
<br>
My proposal is rotation, or taking a break.  (And the break can be shortened too, it doesn't have to be 6 months, but it should be longer than a month)<br>
<br>
More thoughts..........<br>
